These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, soy-milk, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, azure, lavender, amber
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, rock-climbing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, musical, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, jazz, rock
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, lizard, mouse, rabbit
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, car, skateboard, scooter
 1. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes azure##1
 3. the person who likes amber is the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes azure##1
 5. the person driving the skateboard is between the person driving the helicopter and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching musical movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
12. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
13. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the fan of rock##1
14. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
16. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
17. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
18. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the scooter##1
19. the fan of folk is the person who likes apricot##1
20. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
21. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite        | soy-milk   | 7up         | iced-tea  |
| Color          | lavender         | azure   | apricot   | amber |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles    | video-games | drawing   |
| Movie-Genre   | action        | adventure  | satire      | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz          | rock       | folk        | ambient   |
| Pet           | rabbit        | mouse      | goldfish    | lizard    |
| Transport         | scooter | skateboard | helicopter      | car   |

