.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, rose, tulip
There 4 different types of food: banana, papaya, plum, pumpkin
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, western, martial-arts, horror
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, italian, malaysian
4 different pets are kept: lizard, mouse, rabbit, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey, skateboarding, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, train, trike
 1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
 3. the brazilian is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
 5. the person eating banana is the person driving the helicopter##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
 9. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the bus is the italian##1
12. the dutch is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3
14. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
15. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person eating plum##3
16. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
17. the malaysian is in an even position##4
18. the owner of the mouse is the person driving the trike##1
19. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
20. the person watching epic movies is in an odd position##4
21. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Flower      | balloon-flower         | begonia     | tulip        | rose  |
| Food          | plum          | banana     | pumpkin    | papaya   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic          | martial-arts      | western      | horror   |
| Nationality   | brazilian     | malaysian  | dutch      | italian  |
| Pet           | mouse         | turtle     | lizard     | rabbit   |
| Sport         | skateboarding | volleyball | ice-hockey | climbing |
| Transport     | trike         | helicopter | train      | bus      |

